1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
What if I told you there’s an invisible shield around Earth?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,800
This shield is our magnetic field, or magnetosphere, crucial for life.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:13,600
It deflects solar winds, high-energy particles that could strip away our atmosphere.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:17,600
Without it, Earth would be a barren wasteland like Mars.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:21,600
Thanks to this magnetic shield, life thrives on our planet.

6
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:25,200
But wait, did you know it can also weaken?

7
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:27,600
Curious about how it all works?

8
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:30,400
Like and follow for more science secrets!
